"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\">5.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt; color:#000000;\">   </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\">Tính tổng lập phương các số hạng S = 1</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#000000; vertical-align:super;\">3</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\"> + 2</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#000000; vertical-align:super;\">3</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\"> + … + n</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#000000; vertical-align:super;\">3</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\">. Với s, n là các số nguyên.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\">6.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt; color:#000000;\">  </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\">Tính tổng các số chẵn hoặc lẻ của số nguyên n.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#000000;\">Ví dụ: Nhập n = 10    →      </span></p>\n"
