"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">1.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt; color:#000000;\">      </span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Viết chương trình xuất ra màn hình dòng chữ ‘Mai truong cua em, xanh sach va than thien!!!’</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">2.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt; color:#000000;\">      </span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Viết chương trình xuất ra màn hình dòng chữ theo yêu cầu sau:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">a.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt; color:#000000;\">   </span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">‘Tap the lop 11A1 chung em’                                   </span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">‘Doan ket, cham ngoan va hoc gioi’</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; font-size:8pt;\"><br /></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt;\">b. </span><img src=\":/Chuong 1/writeln/Hinh 1.png\" /><span style=\" font-size:12pt;\"><br /></span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%;\"><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">3.</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; font-size:7pt; color:#000000;\">                  </span><span style=\" font-size:12pt; color:#000000;\">Viết chương trình cho phép nhập vào chiều dài a, chiều rộng b. Sau đó tính chu vi, diện tích hình chữ nhật từ những dữ kiện nhập vào.        </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; font-size:8pt;\"><br /></p>\n"
