"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">1. Các thành phần cơ bản</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">Mỗi ngôn ngữ lập trình có 3 thành phần cơ bản là </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">Bảng chữ cái</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">, </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">cú pháp</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\"> và </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">ngữ nghĩa</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">a. Bảng chữ cái</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">- Tập hợp kí tự</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\"> được dùng để viết chương trình</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline; color:#363636;\">Ví dụ:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">Trong Pascal bảng chữ cái bao gồm:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:115%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">- Chữ cái thường và chữ cái in hoa tiếng Anh: a...z ; A..Z</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
