"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">+ Shift+ </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">←,</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\"> </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">↑,</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\"> </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">↓,</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\"> </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">→</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">:</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\"> Tô khối.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">+ Shift+Delete: </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">(</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">Cut</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">) Cắt nội dung chọn vào bộ nhớ.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">+ Ctrl+Insert:</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\"> (</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">Copy</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">) Sao chép nd chọn vào bộ nhớ.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">+ Shift+Insert:</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\"> (</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">Paste</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">) Dán nd trong bộ nhớ ra màn hình tại vị trí con trỏ.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">+ Ctrl+K+H:</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\"> Tắt dấu tô khối.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
