"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline; color:#363636;\">Ví dụ 1:</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\"> </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">Để giải phương trình bậc hai: ax</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636; vertical-align:super;\">2</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\"> +bx +c = 0 (a ≠≠ 0 ) ta phải: Tính Delta = b*b - 4*a*c</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">- Nếu Delta &lt; 0 thì phương trình vô nghiệm.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">- Nếu Delta &gt;= 0 thì phương trình có nghiệm.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">Hoặc có thể nói: Nếu Delta &lt; 0 thì phương trình vô nghiệm, ngược lại phương trình có nghiệm.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">Ta có mệnh đề sau:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">- Nếu ... thì ...                                       (Dạng thiếu)</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">- Nếu ... thì ... nếu không thì ...                (Dạng đủ)</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
