"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">Trong đó:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">- Điều kiện: Là biểu thức quan hệ hoặc logic.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
