"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">Xác định bài toán:</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">- Input</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">: N nhập từ bàn phím.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">- Output</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">: Đưa số ngày của năm N ra màn hình.</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-style:italic; color:#0000ff;\">program</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-style:italic; color:#363636;\"> Nam_nhuan;</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
