"<p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">- Các thủ tục dùng để </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">đọc dữ liệu</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\"> </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">từ tệp </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; font-style:italic; color:#363636;\">tepA</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-style:italic; color:#363636;\"> </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">có thể như sau: </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#0000ff;\">read</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">(tepA, A, B, C); hoặc  </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#0000ff;\">readln</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">(tepA, X, Y);</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
