"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">ALT+X: </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">Thoát khỏi Turbo Pascal (FILE/Exit) .</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">ALT+F9:</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\"> Dịch chương trình và sửa lỗi cú pháp (nếu có) (RUN/Run).</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">CTRL+F9: </span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\">Thực hiện chạy chương trình. </span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:150%; background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\" font-size:13pt; font-weight:600; color:#363636;\">SHIFT+Del:</span><span style=\" font-size:13pt; color:#363636;\"> Tương ứng với lệnh Cut (menu EDIT).</span><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\"> </span></p>\n"
